               <p>I am a <rs id="t17880507-14-viclabel60" type="occupation">linen draper</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880507-14-victim145 t17880507-14-viclabel60"></join>, <placeName id="t17880507-14-crimeloc61">No. 23, Barbican</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17880507-14-crimeloc61" type="placeName" value="No. 23, Barbican"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17880507-14-crimeloc61" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880507-14-off58 t17880507-14-crimeloc61"></join>; on the 21st of April in the evening, in consequence of an information, I watched my window; I saw the prisoner put his hand in at the window, and take out a pair of stockings; the glass had been broke before; I took them from him, and delivered him to the constable.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17880507-14-person147">
                  JOHN
                   EDWARDS
               <interp inst="t17880507-14-person147" type="surname" value="EDWARDS"></interp>
