                     <interp inst="t17880507-14-person147" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a constable; I took charge of the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178805070014"></xptr>prisoner; the prosecutor gave me the stockings; I have had them ever since.</p>
               <p>(Produced and deposed to by the Prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was coming by the window, there were twenty or thirty people round the window; I picked up the stockings, and was looking at them when the prosecutor laid hold of me.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called one witness who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17880507-14-verdict62" type="verdictDescription">
